divs: Sighting Details This object was not seen when I took the pic. There wasn't any noise or aircraft in the area when I took the pictures.When I showed the pics around to some of the guys said they have seen something like it in Afghanistan. I have seen white balls of light at night before but nothing like this thing.
Summary: The object was not visible when picture was taken. There absolutely were no aircraft around.
